gw.api.domain.account

Interface AccountSyncedField<S extends AccountSyncable,T>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DateAwareAccountSyncedField<S,T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAccountSyncedFieldImpl, AbstractDateAwareAccountSyncedFieldImpl

    public interface AccountSyncedField<S extends AccountSyncable,T>
    Handles access between a field on an account-level entity that is associated with a field on a policy-level (AccountSyncable) entity.
